        <num>CC 645</num>
        <heading>645.  Regulation of the servitude</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 645.  Regulation of the servitude.
A right of use is regulated by application of the rules governing usufruct and predial servitudes to the extent that their application is compatible with the rules governing a right of use servitude.</p>
        </content>
